= block_with_caption :bottom, :class=>'video-block'
  - if video_iframe?
    iframe [
        src=video_uri
        width=(attr :width)
        height=(attr :height)
        frameborder=0
        allowfullscreen=!(option? 'nofullscreen') ]
  - else
    video [
        src=video_uri
        width=(attr :width)
        height=(attr :height)
        poster=(media_uri(attr :poster) if attr? :poster)
        autoplay=(option? 'autoplay')
        muted=(option? 'muted')
        controls=!(option? 'nocontrols')
        loop=(option? 'loop') ]
      | Your browser does not support the video tag.
